      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly gotta see this beauty in person to believe it. It looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom\u2014I've babied it since day one! It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition with not a single scratch or smudge in sight. I\u2019m really looking for a good home for it, and I promise you won't find one cleaner than this. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
