    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve the visceral performance of its S54 power plant. This 3.2L high-revving inline-six features a refined VANOS system and updated rod bearings, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the powerband. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a reinforced rear subframe and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. The suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances, utilizing refreshed bushings and dampers for razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in flawless Carbon Black over a pristine Cinnamon Nappa leather interior, this specimen exhibits zero oxidation or mechanical fatigue. A turn-key acquisition for the discerning enthusiast seeking a mechanically synchronized, showroom-quality icon.",
      "price": 44500.0,
